org.jmxtrans.embedded

Class QueryAttribute

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jmxtrans.embedded.QueryAttribute

  • public class QueryAttribute
extends Object
    Describe a JMX MBean attribute to collect and hold the attribute collection logic.

    Collected values are sent to a BlockingQueue for later export to the target monitoring systems (see collectMetrics(javax.management.ObjectName, Object, long, java.util.Queue)).

    Author:
    Cyrille Le Clerc, Jon Stevens
